{"tid":1422480,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"重要！！！雨褸會係黎緊一樣重要裝備！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-06T10:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:43:06.000Z","uid":47541,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3235bc47f329e3a25b903e30e967bb99b56c4510","tid":1422480,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"呢兩日已經見到狗狗嘗試用顏色水<br />\n<br />\n雖然暫時佢地只係成功射中自己友，實戰當中見到射程都有一定限制。但難保佢地吸收完經驗可能用高空攻勢或水炮車，噴到一身都係顏料，再慢慢追捕，而顏色水就會成為最有力既證據比佢去拘捕同起訴你！<br />\n<br />\n所以，各位會發夢既人最好袋定件雨褸，可以有效咁cover身體大部分位置，再加埋其他裝備保護，皮膚接觸到既機會已經大大減少！<br />\n<br />\n當然替換衣物變裝都係常識，而雨褸咁輕，帶定做多個保險，用完又一除就丟得走真係唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有其他防顏色水既方法都歡迎討論（之前有巴打講過黑色垃圾袋，但太厚太焗，影響活動能力，實在係唔建議）"},{"pid":"36cf8d5fd198ad432ac32da4c3334dbcc6a28356","tid":1422480,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:59:24.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"4acc5c591bbcff485eb745be84df6c783a3399a6","tid":1422480,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:59:34.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"ed96f97a11d5d2a32ff7668ec4645b8ee418f16e","tid":1422480,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:00:04.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"75a821d904e86d276711e682d1b9c8dd44cd51dc","tid":1422480,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"724d935e95d2947a07e03cdaf2e8e70d13c34c8f","tid":1422480,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:01:04.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"c5de70200560ac53503f24cf01ad8706a37286ae","tid":1422480,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"61e9abb877acd4367b4332d47b094c1cb0dd3454","tid":1422480,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:01:27.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"56c08ea1692748fcddede5d0b2093cea22e6512e"